id: pm-eg9k
title: Document search eval golden-query harness usage in TESTING.md
description: "tests/search-eval/golden-queries.json and the reindex --eval --eval-fixtures flow exist as an advisory CI gate (ci.yml line 212-216, continue-on-error: true). The harness is tested (tests/unit/search-advanced-runtime.spec.ts line 352) but TESTING.md has no explanation of how to use it, extend it, or interpret nDCG scores. New contributors to the search stack will not know this capability exists or how to add queries."
