body: "## Context\nCI gates (ci.yml lines 211-216) runs:\n```\nnode dist/cli.js install search-advanced --project --json\nnode dist/cli.js reindex --mode keyword --eval --eval-fixtures tests/search-eval/golden-queries.json --json\n```\nwith continue-on-error: true (advisory only).\n\ntests/search-eval/golden-queries.json exists with seeded fixture data.\n\ndocs/TESTING.md has no section on search quality evaluation or golden queries.\ndocs/COMMANDS.md has no mention of --eval or --eval-fixtures flags on reindex.\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n- TESTING.md has a 'Search quality evaluation' section explaining:\n  - location of golden-queries.json\n  - how to run locally: reindex --eval --eval-fixtures\n  - how to add new golden queries\n  - advisory nature (continue-on-error in CI)\n- COMMANDS.md reindex section mentions --eval and --eval-fixtures flags\n\n## Evidence\n.github/workflows/ci.yml lines 211-216; tests/search-eval/golden-queries.json; tests/unit/search-advanced-runtime.spec.ts line 352; docs/TESTING.md: no mention of eval/golden-queries"
